    "body": "With the recent changes in the process, it is highly recommended to create a discussion thread at Fellowship of Ethereum Magicians instead of \"Issue\" of this repo and add that FEM link to be updated to the proposal in \"Discussions-To\" section. \r\nThis helps to have the history of discussion in a single place that could be easily referred to even after the proposal is \"Final\".\r\n\r\nJust FYI - another important change is that a proposal needs to be moved to \"Review\" status before it can be moved in the \"Last Call\". So if/when the proposal is ready for review, please be sure to create a pull request for the appropriate status change. \r\n\r\n",
